courses.name: English
courses.description: TII is pleased to offer General English courses for adults this Fall. The English program at TII will help hone your skills and increase your confidence using the English language in both professional and individual settings.

courses.name: Information Technology (IT)
courses.description: This course is designed to provide students with a working knowledge of computer concepts and essential skills necessary for work and communication in today's society. Students will learn safety, security, and ethical issues in computing and social networking.

courses.name: Mather tongue
courses.description: This course includes both the content and the pedagogy of the mother tongue as well as its underlying theoretical assumptions and frameworks that support its being a foundation for learning of the additional languages of Filipino and English and developing stronger literacy skills of learners.

courses.name: FrontEnd (IT) Web Developing
courses.description: In our FrontEnd course, we will learn to work with HTML, CSS, SCSS, Bootstrap, JavaScript, jQuery, VueJS, APIs, etc. You can study our course ONLINE or OFFLINE. The choice is yours.
